                    <div class="article-date">
            7 February 2012          </div>
                              <h1 class="title inf_class" data-analyticsid="/blogs/the-staggers/2012/02/monarchy-jubilee-media-public"><!-- @Title --> The monarchy is more secure than ever </h1>
          <span property="dc:title" content="The monarchy is more secure than ever " class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span><div class="field field-name-field-subheadline field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>The uncomfortable truth for republicans is that public attitudes to the monarchy have barely shifted</p>
</div></div></div>

		  </header>
        <aside class="large-3 columns article-author" style="padding-bottom:0;">
                        <div class="multiple-author-images">

                                  <div class="author-avatar"><img src="/web/20190811003553im_/https://www.newstatesman.com/nsauthorplaceholder.jpg"></div>
                
                
              </div>
          <div class="author-byline"><!-- @Author -->
            By <a href="/web/20190811003553/https://www.newstatesman.com/writers/314640">Sunder Katwala</a>          </div>
                  </aside>
        <!-- .article-author -->

       <div class="featured-image clearfix"><span>                        </span>
             <div style="position:relative; top:-2em;"> 			  </div>
      </div>
      
    </div>
    <!-- .featured-image -->

      </div>
      <!-- .row -->

      <div class="row">
        <div class="large-3 columns article-left-column">
          <div class="full-height-column">
