              <li class="reddit-button st_reddit_hcount"><a target="_blank" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20190811003553/http://www.reddit.com/submit?url=https://www.newstatesman.com/blogs/the-staggers/2012/02/monarchy-jubilee-media-public&amp;title=The" monarchy is more secure than ever> <span class="stButton"> <span class="reddit-button st_reddit_hcount"> &nbsp;</span> <span class="stArrow"><span class="stBubble_hcount">
